@quotation
Permission is granted to copy, distribute and/or modify this document
under the terms of the GNU Free Documentation License, Version 1.3
or any later version published by the Free Software Foundation.
@end quotation
@end copying

@c This section tells 'install-info' where to place this manual in the
@c main system directory.
@dircategory Software development
@direntry
* $PKG_TARNAME: ($PKG_TARNAME).      $PKG_DESCRIPTION
@end direntry

@titlepage
@title $PKG_NAME Manual
@subtitle for version @value{VERSION}, @value{UPDATED}
@author $AUTHOR_NAME (@email{$TEXINFO_EMAIL})
@page
@vskip 0pt plus 1filll
@insertcopying
@end titlepage

@c Generates the Table of Contents.
@contents

@node Top
@top $PKG_NAME Manual

This manual documents the usage of @command{$PKG_TARNAME}.

@menu
* Invocation::          How to run @command{$PKG_TARNAME}.
* Reporting Bugs::      How to report bugs.
@end menu

@node Invocation
@chapter Invocation

@command{$PKG_TARNAME} demonstrates a standard GNU build system.

@example
$PKG_TARNAME [@var{option}]...
@end example

@c man begin OPTIONS
@table @option
@item --help
Display a help message and exit.

@item --version
Output version information and exit.
@end table
@c man end

@node Reporting Bugs
@chapter Reporting Bugs

Report bugs to: @email{$TEXINFO_EMAIL}
@bye
